Thank you for your offer! Please confirm your email address by opening the link

http://letsintegrate.de/<%= @locale %>/offers/<%= @offer.id %>/confirm?token=<%= @offer.confirmation_token %>

<%- if @offer.phone_required? %>
and enter the two parts of the confirmation code in the two text fields on the page.
The part one of the code has been sent by SMS to <%= @offer.phone %>, the part
two is

    <%= @offer.part_two_confirmation_code %>
<%- else %>
and enter the confirmation code

    <%= @offer.confirmation_token %>
<%- end %>

